Global Haloxyfop-P-methyl Market Insights
Haloxyfop-P-methyl Market size was valued at USD 0.3 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Haloxyfop-P-methyl Market Overview
The Haloxyfop-P-methyl market is expected to reach a market value of USD 500 million by 2028, with a growing demand in the agriculture sector for herbicides. This compound is primarily used to control grass weeds in crops such as oilseeds and vegetables. The increasing focus on improving crop yields and ensuring sustainable farming practices is likely to drive the growth of the market. As of 2023, the global market size is estimated at USD 300 million, with a steady growth rate of 6% annually. This market expansion is attributed to the rising need for effective weed control solutions in modern agriculture practices.

